{"id":559549,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/【网络民议】郭文贵的人生轨迹/","date":"2017-05-22T15:18:45Z","modified":"2017-05-23T17:22:56Z","title":"【网络民议】谁都知道郭文贵是国家安全系统的人","content":"<p>以下评论选自推特，截图评论来自新浪微博：</p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/creek_wind/status/866567603241705472</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">潘石屹妇唱夫随，都在微博开怼郭文贵，目前还没叫停，下面评论非常精彩，有兴趣的可以去看看🤣🤣墙内本来实施静默战略，今天是对小潘开放了，这究竟是为了黑郭呢还是对老王进行高级黑呢？吃瓜党也拿不准了😯 <a href=\"https://t.co/Jq8Cil6MBH\">pic.twitter.com/Jq8Cil6MBH</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 仧长老 (@changzhanglao) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/changzhanglao/status/866578809058803712?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559572\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.04.31.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"507\" height=\"425\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.04.31.png 563w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.04.31-300x252.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 507px) 100vw, 507px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559573\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.02.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"380\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.02.png 593w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.02-300x225.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559574\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.18.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"508\" height=\"417\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.18.png 575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.18-300x246.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559575\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.34.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"508\" height=\"422\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.34.png 578w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.34-300x249.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 508px) 100vw, 508px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559576\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.54.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"510\" height=\"355\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.54.png 563w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.05.54-300x209.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px\" /></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/WheatFieldes/status/866570227777187840</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">谁都知道郭文贵是国家安全系统的人，可以随便的去窃听。&#8212; 那麼他當然知道真相</p>\n<p>&mdash; tax_free (@tax_free) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/tax_free/status/866550081058516992?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">哈哈，没错，越多人回应越好，回不回应都是帮了郭，太厉害了郭文贵，替我们出了口气。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 姬存希 (@qXP4IAJKK7U5WEH) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/qXP4IAJKK7U5WEH/status/866577238929530881?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">潘石屹：对郭文贵造谣的回应 ~~~~ 评论全删掉了，有猫腻</p>\n<p>&mdash; 香水的百宝箱 (@key69492096) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/key69492096/status/866576923064811520?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">在中国开放的几十年<br />哪个富商不是官商合作？<br />没有官的合作而发大财的？<br />哪个女人不是靠床上<br />而获得名与利的？<br />脸皮厚<br />不要脸<br />出卖肉体与灵魂<br />才是发财之道！<br />至少郭讲出了事实真相<br />浪子回头金不换<br />放下屠刀立地成佛<br />所以越来越多有良知的人<br />相信浪子郭文贵</p>\n<p>&mdash; 宇峒 (@xYsfknBXPT6M0jo) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/xYsfknBXPT6M0jo/status/866552743221055489?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/KzUJX4CNyEnMWpC/status/866585249576136704</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">潘石屹微博粉丝2000万，张欣1000万。潘张二人在微博替郭文贵打广告！</p>\n<p>&mdash; 阿里妞妞 (@aliniuniu) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aliniuniu/status/866584303202844676?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/combeini/status/866583970963529729</p>\n<p>https://twitter.com/steven_boshi/status/866583337313255424</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">潘石屹：“但刚看了开头就看不下去了，郭文贵的视频又臭又长”——连看都不看完，怎么知道别人都说了自己什么坏话？郭文贵也没有发过多少文字内容。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 自由飞鱼 (@FlyFish8964) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/FlyFish8964/status/866583197341102085?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">小潘儿这辟谣文章有点假啊。什么叫刚开始听人说郭文贵造你谣没当回事，吹牛逼呢？郭文贵都成了官场炸药包了，您听造您谣都没当回事儿？这个太假了。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 小狼 (@quanyongxian) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/quanyongxian/status/866568313232424961?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">😱😱😱完了，我没理智了，因为潘石屹说：“相信任何一个有理智的人都不会相信郭文贵这些低级骗人的鬼话。”😂😂😂 <a href=\"https://t.co/bmqmA7ffDN\">pic.twitter.com/bmqmA7ffDN</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 清朗 (@qinglang0207) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/qinglang0207/status/866549285868806144?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">郭文贵熟知官场，房地产，金融领域，而这三种恰恰是当今中国的三座大山，除了疾病，中国人的所有苦难几乎都源自这里。郭如果持续与当局对抗，拉更多当事人入局，公开在网络平台攻击对手或自我辩解，都将是历史性的。以公知示人的潘石屹是中国最成功的商人现在出来公开较量这是好事。 <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/%E4%BD%86%E8%BF%98%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%8D%E5%A4%9F%E4%B9%B1?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#但还是不够乱</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 阿拉不善 (@majunlive) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/majunlive/status/866570747694665728?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">谁能保证郭文贵爆出来的“料”的真实性？有专业权威的第三方机</p>\n<p>构为其背书吗？是否构成完整清晰的证据链？中共的制度性腐败明</p>\n<p>白人都知道，但是既然指名道姓，就要拿出经得起检验的证据，而</p>\n<p>不是靠这些三流地摊文学里面用的耸人听闻的套路，靠人民群众脑</p>\n<p>补出来的情节来博取眼球和同情。</p>\n<p>&mdash; 全子 (@dczd2) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/dczd2/status/866553111044804608?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">潘石屹：对郭文贵造谣的回应  谁都知道郭文贵是国家安全系统的人，可以随便的去窃听，可以随便的去抓人。谁都知道郭文贵背后的“老领导”势力很大，在中国比天还大，谁敢得罪这样的人呢？但人世间还有正义。中国的天空中还有太阳，不能永远黑暗下去。<a href=\"https://t.co/TOtvK8TUwh\">https://t.co/TOtvK8TUwh</a> <a href=\"https://t.co/nzQHuuza4T\">pic.twitter.com/nzQHuuza4T</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; freewings (@freewingsw) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/freewingsw/status/866553593955926016?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 22, 2017</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559582\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.31.54.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"419\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.31.54.png 575w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.31.54-300x248.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></p>\n<p><img class=\"alignleft wp-image-559583\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.32.27.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"506\" height=\"414\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.32.27.png 583w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-22-11.32.27-300x245.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 506px) 100vw, 506px\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-23-03.24.03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"604\" height=\"473\" class=\"alignleft size-full wp-image-559599\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-23-03.24.03.png 604w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-23-03.24.03-300x235.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 604px) 100vw, 604px\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/Screenshot-2017-05-23-03.24.31.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"582\" height=\"448\" class=\"alignleft size-large wp-image-559600\" srcset=\"https://chinadig